<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>拓展老师杨龙龙向全体教职工介绍游戏规则</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201111/ffe7dc039c3f416e9af09228939121db.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201111/f888e34e5ce54cbfbb275169fe5d37a8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
